{"tid":2149623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"出色裁判官系列：蘇惠德","createTime":"2020-08-10T13:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T03:19:02.000Z","uid":246828,"like":210,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"865d0e04d03beee5d81fc79104abcc82062dc6e0","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:24:04.000Z","msg":"//警方今早突襲《蘋果日報》大樓並取走多箱文件，根據法庭批出的搜查令，警方獲授權進入大樓以調查有關涉嫌違反「港版國安法」的勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國家安全罪以及串謀欺詐罪，手令涵蓋包括壹傳媒有限公司及《蘋果日報》慈善基金等19間公司，警方有權取走除新聞材料外的文件或檔案。<br />\n<br />\n搜查令申請由警員編號16281的商業罪案調查科高級督察Fung Chun-Yi提出，<span class=\"red\"><strong>於8月7日由西九龍裁判法院總裁判官蘇惠德批出</span></strong>。<span class=\"orange\"><strong>手令指，有合理理由懷疑位於將軍澳工業邨駿盈街8號的蘋果日報大樓內有書本、文件、以及該些書本或文件的任何部份，相當可能對調查涉嫌違反《國安法》第29條「勾結外國或者境外勢力危害國安全罪」，以及香港法例第200章《刑事罪行條例》的「串謀欺詐罪」有調查價值</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n手令範圍涵蓋《蘋果日報》慈善基金、壹傳媒有限公司、壹動畫工作室有限公司、蘋果速銷有限公司等19間公司，除新聞材料外，警方可以搜查、接管甚至扣留在大樓內所得的關於此19間公司的商業營運紀錄、會計及人事文件、數碼檔案及設備、公司工具，以及任何其他有關的文件。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"orange\"><strong>法庭授權警方進入、有需要時破門闖入、或強行進入《蘋果日報》大樓，並搜查、接管甚至可以扣留任何看似對調查有價值的書籍及文件</span></strong>，限期至9月6日，除非延期否則會自動失效。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/JALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FJALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM%2F&d=6XXjbPj9602%2BpZUfgYO1mBV%2B9HGzyIzIqBo2vIhly3s%3D&h=7327ae05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FJALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM%2F&h=a5ee8db6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/JALAKW3FLIHWLBPDZCLWDM7KNM/</a>"},{"pid":"534325fefa93ba30b38978d577f3154f92d667f0","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":52,"dislike":11,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7c8708d22c8719de89e903635af7b39fae651906","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":59,"dislike":8,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"蘇惠德傑出事蹟:<br />\n<br />\n- <span class=\"orange\">鐳射筆少年案裁決前修改控罪，指少年參與和平遊行無理由攜帶鐳射筆及爛遮，認為少年攜帶鐳射筆及爛遮出現示威現場唯一合理推斷為少年有意圖用其傷害警員，裁定少年管有攻擊性武器罪成並重判少年入更生中心</span>，拒絕少年等候上訴保釋；<br />\n<br />\n- <span class=\"orange\">鄭若驊丈夫潘樂陶僭建案，輕判潘罰款2萬元</span>；<br />\n<br />\n- 吳文遠向梁振英掉三文治案，裁定吳文遠罪成，吳文遠其後上訴得直"},{"pid":"580c7e0c2d3c0b7445057cabbf5b5abb5b9e63c6","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:26:03.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d34ab137d3953e9d93b47f7836457ef6f22309","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:26:25.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e566c538bc33b3da367c0f0dbff3d03175be8dc","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:26:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"962c487cb32acf7298a1f476053917b3ad2df5b2","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:27:22.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72eaac1a655f7d4a58f26c24ae8bb7c18d04cac","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27164026e3d5b2ee8c353a01b9f840a1304564ca","tid":2149623,"uid":114072,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"534325fefa93ba30b38978d577f3154f92d667f0","tid":2149623,"uid":246828,"like":52,"dislike":11,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:24:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T13:28:01.000Z","msg":"竟然真係大學生嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0546541719f86c7777999c3b635a46faa74e573","t